      "description": "Honk uses a vibrant, high-contrast visual system where bold primary colors make the interface pop. The design relies on a striking blue canvas accented by bright yellow highlights and white text, creating an energetic and direct communication style. Typography is bold and casual, contributing to an approachable, fun atmosphere. Most elements are flat with minimal shadows, emphasizing clarity and quick interaction.",
      "customSections": [
        {
          "title": "Agent Prompt Guide",
          "content": "Quick Color Reference:\ntext: #111111\nbackground: #008fff\nborder: #ffffff\naccent: #ffe400\nprimary action: no distinct CTA color\n\nExample Component Prompts:\n1. Create a hero headline block: Honk Header weight 700, 52px, letter-spacing -0.62px, text color Sunshine Accent (#ffe400); immediately followed by body text using Honk Sans, 19px, weight 400, text color Paper White (#ffffff).\n2. Create a footer link: Honk Sans, 14px, weight 400, text color Paper White (#ffffff), no underline, on a Sky Canvas (#008fff) background. It should use a 6px border radius if it were to become a filled button."
